snippet.title: Moshi Monsters - Moshlings Theme Park US Trailer - Out Now
snippet.description:
Get the sequel to the Number 1 best-selling Nintendo DS title, Moshi Monsters Moshling Zoo! Mind Candy presents: Moshlings Theme Park!

Rebuild The Theme Park - Prepare for goopendous thrills and spills as you explore and restore the legendary Moshlings Theme Park

Find The Lost Moshlings - Get collecting as you round up 60 lost Moshlings. Play mini-games to unlock hints & tips to help you in your search.

Experience Monsterific Rides - Hit splat-tastic high scores as you guide your Monster to glory aboard the wildest coasters, karts, slides and rides

Unlock Secret Items - Go for gold playing wacky mini games and unlock monsterific new content with hidden codes 

Monster Rewards - Trade Theme Park goodies via Streetpass and find hidden Moshlings using the exclusive ARG (3DS only)

Moshi Monsters is a free and highly innovative new virtual world and online game, where people adopt and care for their very own pet monster.

Adopt a Moshi Monster: http://MoshiMonsters.com/

Like: http://Facebook.com/MoshiMonsters

Follow: http://twitter.com/MoshiMonsters

The Official Store: http://Store.MoshiMonsters.com/

Get the Moshi Monsters Album: http://full.sc/P1lRyL 

Watch Moshi TV: http://MoshiTV.com/ 

Moshi Monsters - Moshlings Theme Park US Trailer - Out October 30th - Pre-Order Now

http://www.youtube.com/user/moshimonsters
